CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 16, 1962, pg. 22, reads: "Alpha Wives' Fete - The success of the swank bridge luncheon given by the Alpha Wives, last Saturday, at Hotel Webster Hall, was largely due to the work of the above committee. Left to right, seated: Mmes. Doris Brown, Mary Jane Page, Cecile Springer, president; Mary Page and Madelyn Hairston, general chairman.  Standing in rear are Mmes. Alyce Parr and Wilhelmina Brown... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Members of Alpha Wives seated from left: Doris Clark Brown (Moody), Mary Jane Mitchell Page, Cecile Springer, Mary Page, Madelyn Hairston; standing: Alyce Parr and Wilhelmina Byrd Brown, gathered in Webster Hall for annual bridge luncheon
